Title: Step 1: Finding the Marksman’s Lodge
Text: I need to continue my training to earn the Marksmanship License. Marcus Eldridge has directed me to the Marksman’s Lodge and Highland Shooting Range, where I’ll meet Darius Blackwood, a top instructor. The Lodge and Range are located near the top of the south mountain on Monsalac Island, southeast of Chaseals Village. I should head there to begin my training.
CompleteText: I've found the Marksman’s Lodge and Highland Shooting Range. Time to meet Darius Blackwood and start my training.
